name: InkAnalysisParagraph
description: Represents ink analysis data for an identified paragraph formed by ink strokes.

properties.name: id
properties.description: Gets the ID of the InkAnalysisParagraph object.

properties.name: lines
properties.description: Gets the ink analysis lines in this ink analysis paragraph.

methods.name: load
methods.description: Fills the proxy object created in JavaScript layer with property and object values specified in the parameter.

parameters.name: param
parameters.description: Accepts parameter and relationship names as delimited string or an array. Or, provide [loadOption](loadoption.md) object.
